text: I love cooking meals for myself
I love waking up early in the morning
I love making time for my habits and hobbies
I love taking a shower every morning
I adore doing my morning routine and how it feels
I love a good workout
I am an impressive combination of obscenely original very spontaneous and super fun
I am always laughing or smiling (if I am not in a bad mood)
I have my routines that I can't be broken from (you can't break me from)
I have superb self-hygiene and make a point of being proud of it to myself
My energy is rich and real, but also light fun, and funny
I make deep connections with others
I am humble kind and generous
I pay attention to how various things impact me and I structure my life accordingly
I am always the first to offer help to someone in need
I am very strong, physically
I am thoughtful and wise
I take care when getting dressed in the morning
When I am having a bad day I work out as my first line of defense
I pay attention to myself, to my body, to its needs
I do not hesitate to make my brain work hard
I reach my potential
I am a safe space for anyone to be with or confide in
I can be serious, but usually, I am not
If someone needs something they can't quite do themselves I am among the first to come to mind
I push myself but I am very kind and nurturing to myself no matter what
I love eating but specifically eating healthy
I take joy in organizing parties and get together for/with my friends
I take action to give myself energy
I choose how I spend my time wisely
